OL,3,GWales
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FCloudy and
OL,6,Fdamp overnight with outbreaks of rain
OL,7,Fspreading across the country, locally
OL,8,Fturning heavy over the hills at times.
OL,9,FWidely misty and murky with coastal
OL,10,Fand hill fog. Warm and muggy.
OL,11,
OL,12,CWednesday:FCloudy and misty with rain
OL,13,Fin the morning. Rain easing as the day
OL,14,Fprogresses with brighter spells
OL,15,Fdeveloping as low cloud lifts,
OL,16,Fprimarily in the north. Feeling humid.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
