OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Thursday to Saturday:
OL,6,FUnsettled and humid in the northwest
OL,7,Fon Thursday and Friday with further
OL,8,Frain and low cloud. Brighter spells in
OL,9,Fthe east. Feeling fresher on Saturday
OL,10,Fwith more widespread sunny spells.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
